@startuml
skinparam Shadowing true
skinparam RoundCorner 5
skinparam MaxMessageSize 250

participant "Single Page Application" as SPA #LightBlue

box "api-gateway" #5D6D7E
    participant "Route Configuration" as RC #White
end box

participant "target-service" as TS #F4ECF7

group #LightCyan Проксирование публичного запроса\nПорт: 4004 → target-service (StripPrefix=1)

    SPA -> RC ++: **[1]** HTTP Request
    RC -> RC: Поиск маршрута в application.yml\nJwtValidation filter NOT FOUND

    RC -> TS ++: **[2]** Proxy Request\n(/auth/... → /... via StripPrefix=1)

    alt #MistyRose Целевой сервис недоступен
        TS --[#red]> RC: <color:#red>Connection Refused / Timeout</color>
        RC --[#red]> SPA: <color:#red>500 INTERNAL SERVER ERROR</color>
    end

    TS --[#green]> RC --: **[3]** HTTP Response
    RC --[#green]> SPA: **[4]** Proxy Response

end
@enduml
